node.text:
The Lucas Braathen Racing Camp powered by Atomic is now live! This is a Norwegian u-12 and u-14 camp that is being held over the final two weekends of June. Due to Covid, this year is only available those residing in Norway. To get a spot, follow the link in our bio. Hope to see you there! #weareskiing #lucasbraathenracingcamp #redster #racingcamp

@pinheiiiroo

node.title: Lucas Braathen Racing Camp Powered by Atomic Skis

node.text:
We are skiers. We are sisters and mothers, nurses and teachers, managers and engineers. We are young and old. We ski big mountains and small ones. We race through slalom gates, we plunge into deep powder. We crash. We ski hard. We ski smoothly. Slow. And fast. We ski to connect with nature, to reach new goals, to bond with community, to set our spirits free. There is no right or wrong way to paint lines down the mountain, and so many reasons why #sheskis

Share your story #sheskis
